page.title: 20THE COMPILERS.
page.content: This section of the Domesday Project was compiled by the following people. Mr.B.F.D.WILLIAMS.Mrs.J.DELFINO. Mr.R.H.TAYLOR.Mr.H.A.BARROW. DONNA MILLS,ANGELA FOSTER,MILES BROWN,HILARY PRIMETT,HEATHER GOODWIN,LEE COOPER,ROBERT CHAPMAN,GARY GLOVER,DYLAN ELLIOTT,SALLY HOWLETT,DARREN MEDHURST,NIGEL DIMMOCK, JEREMY COSTELLO,KURT BROAD,JENNIFER DOY,DANIEL WINGAD,KATIE THOMPSON,JULIE STEVENS,VANESSA MARSHALL,HARVEY TAYLOR,IAN TARONI,JOANNE TOTMAN,SUSAN BURDETT,JILL DAVISON,CHERYL PATRICK, TRACEY WRIGHT. Almost all of these people are concerned in one way or another with the Ailwyn Community School,Ramsey which is in Cambridgeshire.
